{"tid":298387,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"薄瓜瓜獲律師資格 轉往加拿大謀生","createTime":"2017-06-26T08:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T08:57:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11ce53e25722ad9b1e61e116b662879f8df945a1","tid":298387,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T08:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20130825/large/25la1p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20130825%2Flarge%2F25la1p04.jpg&h=8e540883&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170625/56874346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170625%2F56874346&d=Scun4cOwK9E7LDUnoSYBORFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=d148bc90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170625%2F56874346&h=01a09301\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170625/56874346</a><br />\n<br />\n海外華文媒體引述消息指，重慶市委前書記薄熙來的兒子薄瓜瓜，近日在美國紐約取得律師資格後，已持獲得延期的中國護照到加拿大謀生。<br />\n<br />\n明鏡新聞網指出，現年29歲的薄瓜瓜去年5月在哥倫比亞大學法學院畢業，並取得博士學位，11月通過美國的律師資格考試後，開始在紐約的律師事務所實習。<br />\n<br />\n薄熙來涉受賄、貪污、濫用職權被判無期徒刑，谷開來則涉殺英國商人海伍德，同樣被判無期徒刑，薄瓜瓜失去父母庇蔭，或可能會坐食山崩，所以亦會想辦法養活自己。海外媒體早前報道，薄瓜瓜曾向哥倫比亞大學的同學稱，畢業後趕緊抓工作，好養活自己，而他早前亦表明不希望當官或者經商。<br />\n<br />\n明鏡新聞網"}]}